## 1. Task Intent Interpretation

### 1.1 Problem Summary

NuttyFans has an existing database schema in `docs/04-DATABASE-SCHEMA.md` that requires:
- Critical analysis and validation
- Gap identification for scalability (1M+ users)
- Verification against business requirements
- Assessment of admin/operational readiness

**This is an analysis task, not a blind redesign.**

### 1.2 Business Context

Per `docs/01-BRD.md` and `docs/02-PRD.md`:
- Target: 10,000 creators, 500,000 users (Year 1)
- Scale: 100,000 creators, 5M users (Year 2)
- Revenue model: 15% commission on transactions
- Core flows: Subscriptions, PPV, Tips, Paid DMs, Live Streaming

### 1.3 Scope Boundaries

| In Scope | Out of Scope |
|----------|--------------|
| Schema analysis | Writing migrations |
| Gap identification | Choosing database vendor |
| Requirements validation | Implementing ORM models |
| Scalability assessment | Admin panel UI |
| Indexing review | Feature-specific logic |
| Normalization review | |

